ack which help guide our programing initiatives and pave the way for the future. As such, membership is requested in order to participate in the free programs offered at Parya.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n	Benefits of being a Friend of Parya&nbsp;include:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		special admission prices to events offered at Parya</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		discounts on certain programs</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		8 issues of our electronic newsletter</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		discounts at specialized retail and service-based businesses&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		20% discount on rental rates of our facilities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	Parya welcomes people of all backgrounds, regardless of ethnicity, religion, and physical ability.</p>\";s:20:\"contribution_type_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:20:\"payment_processor_id\";s:1:\"1\";s:19:\"is_credit_card_only\";s:1:\"0\";s:11:\"is_monetary\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"is_recur\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"is_recur_interval\";s:1:\"0\";s:12:\"is_pay_later\";s:1:\"0\";s:14:\"pay_later_text\";s:28:\"I will send payment by check\";s:21:\"is_allow_other_amount\";s:1:\"1\";s:10:\"min_amount\";s:4:\"5.00\";s:10:\"max_amount\";s:7:\"5000.00\";s:14:\"thankyou_title\";s:24:\"Thanks for Your Support!\";s:13:\"thankyou_text\";s:354:\"<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n	Thank you for joining Parya Trillium Foundation. As of this moment you are now an official member of Parya and can take advantage of all of the benefits of Friendship status. You have automatically been signed up to receive announcements from Parya and will be added to our membership roster in the next week or so.</p>\";s:19:\"is_for_organization\";s:1:\"1\";s:16:\"for_organization\";s:47:\"I am contributing on behalf of an organization.\";s:16:\"is_email_receipt\";s:1:\"1\";s:17:\"receipt_from_name\";s:17:\"Parya Memberships\";s:18:\"receipt_from_email\";s:21:\"memberships@parya.org\";s:11:\"bcc_receipt\";s:45:\"memberships@parya.org,webmaster@ideograph.biz\";s:12:\"receipt_text\";s:101:\"Thanks for supporting our Parya with your